---
name: example-fullstack-design-system
description: Complete design system reference for Lazy Golfing including Miami Vice color palette (hot pink/cyan/purple for dark mode, coral/orange/yellow for light mode), typography, spacing, component patterns (shadcn/ui), glassmorphism effects, GPU-accelerated animations, and WCAG AA accessibility requirements. Use when implementing UI, choosing colors, applying spacing, creating components, or ensuring brand consistency.
---

# Lazy Golfing Design System Reference

**Purpose:** Complete reference for Lazy Golfing's design tokens, colors, typography, spacing, components, and code patterns.

**Design Direction:** Miami Vice Theme (December 2025)
- Neon aesthetics with glassmorphism
- Theme-adaptive colors (different palettes for dark/light modes)
- Gradient text effects with neon glow
- Golf-focused, fun, approachable

**Single Source of Truth:** `/lzg.home/src/lib/theme.ts`

**See Also:** `.claude/skills/lazy-golfing-ux-designer/` for professional design expertise and critique framework.

---

## 🎯 Brand Identity

**Brand Narrative:**
> "Lazy golf for lazy golfers!"
> "Cart golf only!"
>
> Lazy Golfing is the comprehensive golf tracking platform for players who want to have fun. Track rounds, join leagues, compete in tournaments, and connect with playing partners. No walking required. No pretense. Just good golf with good people.

**Voice:**
- Friendly and inclusive
- Self-aware and fun
- Celebrates small wins and funny losses
- Never takes itself too seriously

---

## 🎨 Color Palette

### Primary Brand Colors

**Dark Mode (Neon Miami Vice):**
```css
/* Hot Pink (Primary) */
--brand-pink: #ff0080;
--brand-pink-hsl: 330 100% 50%;

/* Cyan (Secondary) */
--brand-cyan: #00f0ff;
--brand-cyan-hsl: 184 100% 50%;

/* Purple (Accent) */
--brand-purple: #9b59ff;
--brand-purple-hsl: 270 70% 60%;
```

**Light Mode (Warm Sunset):**
```css
/* Coral (Primary) */
--brand-coral: #ff6b6b;
--brand-coral-hsl: 10 100% 65%;

/* Orange (Secondary) */
--brand-orange: #ff7033;
--brand-orange-hsl: 25 100% 55%;

/* Yellow (Accent) */
--brand-yellow: #ffbf00;
--brand-yellow-hsl: 45 100% 55%;
```

### Theme-Adaptive CSS Variables

```css
:root {
  /* Light mode defaults */
  --brand-primary: 25 100% 55%;    /* Orange */
  --brand-secondary: 45 100% 55%;  /* Yellow */
  --brand-accent: 10 100% 65%;     /* Coral */
}

.dark {
  /* Dark mode overrides */
  --brand-primary: 330 100% 55%;   /* Hot Pink */
  --brand-secondary: 184 100% 50%; /* Cyan */
  --brand-accent: 270 70% 60%;     /* Purple */
}
```

### Background & Surface Colors

```css
/* Light Mode */
--background: #ffffff;
--foreground: #0a0a0f;
--card: #ffffff;
--muted: #f5f5f5;

/* Dark Mode */
--background: #0a0a0f;
--foreground: #fafafa;
--card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
--muted: #1a1a1f;
```

### Semantic Colors

```css
/* Success */
--success: #10B981;

/* Warning */
--warning: #F59E0B;

/* Error/Destructive */
--destructive: #EF4444;

/* Info */
--info: #3B82F6;
```

---

## 🌈 Gradients

### Text Gradients

```css
/* Sunset Gradient (Theme-adaptive) */
.gradient-text-sunset {
  background: linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    hsl(var(--brand-primary)) 0%,
    hsl(var(--brand-accent)) 50%,
    hsl(var(--brand-secondary)) 100%
  );
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}

/* Golden Gradient */
.gradient-text-golden {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffbf00 0%, #ff7033 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
```

### Background Gradients

```css
/* Miami Vice Gradient */
.bg-gradient-miami {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff0080 0%, #00f0ff 100%);
}

/* Sunset Gradient */
.bg-gradient-sunset {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff7033 0%, #ff6b6b 50%, #ff0080 100%);
}

/* Glow Effects */
.bg-glow-pink {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.15), transparent 50%);
}

.bg-glow-cyan {
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1), transparent 50%);
}

.bg-glow-mixed {
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.15), transparent 40%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1), transparent 40%);
}
```

---

## ✨ Effects

### Neon Glow

```css
/* Warm glow (sunset colors) */
.neon-glow-warm {
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px hsl(var(--brand-primary) / 0.5);
}

/* Cool glow (cyan) */
.neon-glow-cool {
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px hsl(var(--brand-secondary) / 0.5);
}

/* Golden glow */
.neon-glow-golden {
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 191, 0, 0.4);
}
```

### Glassmorphism

```css
.glass {
  background: hsl(var(--card) / 0.5);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border) / 0.5);
}
```

---

## 📐 Typography

### Font Stack

```css
/* System font stack (performant) */
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
```

### Type Scale

```css
font-size: 12px;  /* xs - captions */
font-size: 14px;  /* sm - small text */
font-size: 16px;  /* base - body (DEFAULT) */
font-size: 18px;  /* lg - subheadings */
font-size: 20px;  /* xl - headings */
font-size: 24px;  /* 2xl - section titles */
font-size: 30px;  /* 3xl - page titles */
font-size: 36px;  /* 4xl - hero titles */
font-size: 48px;  /* 5xl - hero large */
```

---

## 🎭 Spacing & Layout

### Spacing Scale (Tailwind)

```css
space-1: 4px;
space-2: 8px;
space-3: 12px;
space-4: 16px;   /* Default padding */
space-6: 24px;
space-8: 32px;
space-12: 48px;
space-16: 64px;
```

### Border Radius

```css
rounded-sm: 4px;
rounded-md: 8px;
rounded-lg: 12px;
rounded-xl: 16px;
rounded-2xl: 24px;  /* Cards, containers */
rounded-full: 9999px; /* Pills, avatars */
```

### Container Widths

```css
max-w-md: 448px;    /* Modals, small forms */
max-w-lg: 512px;    /* Medium forms */
max-w-xl: 576px;    /* Large forms */
max-w-4xl: 896px;   /* Content pages */
max-w-[1800px];     /* Full-width layouts */
```

---

## 🧩 Component Patterns

### Buttons (shadcn/ui)

```tsx
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';

// Primary action
<Button>Get Started</Button>

// Secondary action
<Button variant="outline">Learn More</Button>

// Destructive
<Button variant="destructive">Delete</Button>

// Ghost (minimal)
<Button variant="ghost">Cancel</Button>
```

### Cards

```tsx
<div className="glass rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
  {/* Content */}
</div>
```

### Header/Footer

```
Single source of truth:
- Header: /lzg.home/src/components/layout/Header.tsx
- Footer: /lzg.home/src/components/layout/Footer.tsx

Never duplicate in pages - they come from layout.tsx
```

---

## 🎬 Animations

### GPU-Accelerated Only

```css
/* Only animate transform and opacity for 60fps */
.animate-fade-in {
  animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
```

### Transitions

```css
/* Standard transition */
transition: all 0.2s ease;

/* For colors/backgrounds */
transition: colors 0.2s ease;
```

---

## ♿ Accessibility (WCAG AA)

### Color Contrast

- **Text on background:** Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio
- **Large text (18px+):** Minimum 3:1 contrast ratio
- **UI components:** Minimum 3:1 contrast ratio

### Focus States

```css
/* Focus ring for all interactive elements */
focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-primary focus:ring-offset-2
```

### Keyboard Navigation

- Tab to navigate interactive elements
- Enter/Space to activate buttons
- Escape to close modals
- Arrow keys for menus

---

## 📁 Asset Organization

```
public/
├── favicons/           # All favicon files
├── images/             # Logo, OG image, photos
│   ├── logo.png
│   └── og-image.jpg    # 1200x630, <1MB
├── patterns/           # SVG patterns
│   └── grid.svg
└── site.webmanifest
```

---

## 🔗 See Also

- `/CLAUDE.md` - Project guidelines
- `/lzg.home/CLAUDE.md` - Frontend patterns
- `/lzg.home/src/lib/theme.ts` - Color configuration (source of truth)
- `/lzg.home/src/lib/metadata.ts` - SEO configuration
- `/lzg.home/src/app/globals.css` - CSS variables
- `.claude/skills/lazy-golfing-ux-designer/` - UX expertise

